{"tid":1206780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[呼籲] 久守必失 必需設立死線 一鼓作氣到底","createTime":"2019-06-12T04:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:33:42.000Z","uid":134385,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac21078bc1c362719da587f47905c08a28061236","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"吸收2014失敗經驗 比政府拖延落去<br />\n最終都會係失敗收場 比人清場<br />\n記住時間越長 士氣越低 <br />\n所以絕對需要設立死線<br />\n如果政府無係死線之前 有任何回應既話 <br />\n所有人一定要有進一步行動!<br />\n<br />\n最後 記住目標一定要撤回條例<br />\n除左搬回惡法 任何形式回應都唔可以視為成功<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一鼓作氣 再而衰 三而竭</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d05eeefc6e4c4f2d466de30896ad1eb13731130","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:05:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffa6a99b5c62760c3c5e5fca9ae1190fca3701ba","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e37f369697c4fd889130485fb65bb9adb36aa7c6","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e98394497414300f5e653f947eeef48afc4e215f","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36a51f487376f96bf0a9081665a11bc3a3bde837","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"一定要死線 絕不妥協"},{"pid":"676bc7c2ba9552908a6224ac7558e16a39edb82f","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82eb967388938343943de5e6c59981fff48596ce","tid":1206780,"uid":97104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:12:31.000Z","msg":"3點"},{"pid":"cc49df832a01dce74a108f67369f42bb4fc79068","tid":1206780,"uid":134385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim